library(data.table)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(ggbreak)
rm(list = ls())

dat <- fread('CHROMM_States.txt') 
eqtl <- read.csv('eqtl_chromtain_fisher_res.csv')
aqtl <- read.csv('aqtl_chromtain_fisher_res.csv')
sqtl <- read.csv('sqtl_chromtain_fisher_res.csv')
eqtl$type <- sapply(strsplit(eqtl$type,'_'),'[',4)
eqtl$type <- gsub('.bed','',eqtl$type,fixed = T)
aqtl$type <- sapply(strsplit(aqtl$type,'_'),'[',4)
aqtl$type <- gsub('.bed','',aqtl$type,fixed = T)
sqtl$type <- sapply(strsplit(sqtl$type,'_'),'[',4)
sqtl$type <- gsub('.bed','',sqtl$type,fixed = T)
eqtl$Type <- 'eQTL'
aqtl$Type <- 'apaQTL'
sqtl$Type <- 'sQTL'
data <- rbind(eqtl,aqtl,sqtl)
data$new_Var1 <- factor(data$type, levels = c('TxFlnk','TssAFlnk','TssA','EnhG','Tx','TxWk','Enh','ZNF.Rpts','Het','TssBiv','BivFlnk','EnhBiv','ReprPC','ReprPCWk','Quies'))
data$stars <- ifelse(data$Pvalue < 0.05/15 & data$OR >1, "*", "")

ggplot(data, aes(x = new_Var1, y = OR, fill = Type)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity",
           width = 0.75,
           position = position_dodge(width = 0.75)) +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymax=high_95_ci, ymin=low_95_ci), color='black', position = position_dodge(0.75), width = 0.4,lwd=0.5) +    
  theme_classic(base_size = 18) +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "Type of QTLs",
                    values = c("#BC3C29","#2D417F","#CB812A")) +
  labs(x = "", y = "OR (Compared with non-xQTLs)", title = "") +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(size = 18, colour = "black", angle = 45, hjust = 1, vjust = 1),  
    axis.text.y = element_text(size = 18, colour = "black"), 
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    legend.position = c("top"),
    legend.justification = "center",
    legend.key.height = unit(2, "mm"),
    legend.key.width = unit(5, "mm"),
  ) +
  scale_y_break(c(10, 16)) + 
  geom_hline(yintercept = 1, lty = 3, lwd = 1, col = "#DC0000B2") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(colour = 'black', angle = 45, hjust = 1, vjust = 1)) +
  geom_text(aes(label = stars), 
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.75), 
            vjust = 0.3,
            size = 10)    
ggsave('Figure 2A.pdf',width=17, height=7)

library(data.table)
library(ComplexHeatmap)
library(RColorBrewer)
library(circlize)
library(ggplot2)
library(gridBase)
rm(list = ls())

eqtl <- fread('eqtl_TF_fisher_res.csv')
eqtl$cell_line <- sapply(strsplit(eqtl$type,'-'),'[',1)
eqtl$tf <- sapply(strsplit(eqtl$type,'-'),'[',2)
eqtl$Tissue <- 'eQTLs enriched in transcription factors'
eqtl <- subset(eqtl,cell_line=='A549' & !tf=='POLR2AphosphoS2')
eqtl <- eqtl[order(eqtl$tf,eqtl$Pvalue,eqtl$OR),]
eqtl <- eqtl[!duplicated(eqtl$tf),]
eqtl <- eqtl[,c('tf','OR','Pvalue')]
names(eqtl) <- c('tf','eQTL','e_p')
aqtl <- fread('aqtl_TF_fisher_res.csv')
aqtl$cell_line <- sapply(strsplit(aqtl$type,'-'),'[',1)
aqtl$tf <- sapply(strsplit(aqtl$type,'-'),'[',2)
aqtl$Tissue <- 'apaQTLs enriched in transcription factors'
aqtl <- subset(aqtl,cell_line=='A549' & !tf=='POLR2AphosphoS2')
aqtl <- aqtl[order(aqtl$tf,aqtl$Pvalue,aqtl$OR),]
aqtl <- aqtl[!duplicated(aqtl$tf),]
aqtl <- aqtl[,c('tf','OR','Pvalue')]
names(aqtl) <- c('tf','apaQTL','a_p')
sqtl <- fread('sqtl_TF_fisher_res.csv')
sqtl$cell_line <- sapply(strsplit(sqtl$type,'-'),'[',1)
sqtl$tf <- sapply(strsplit(sqtl$type,'-'),'[',2)
sqtl$Tissue <- 'sQTLs enriched in transcription factors'
sqtl <- subset(sqtl,cell_line=='A549' & !tf=='POLR2AphosphoS2')
sqtl <- sqtl[order(sqtl$tf,sqtl$Pvalue,sqtl$OR),]
sqtl <- sqtl[!duplicated(sqtl$tf),]
sqtl <- sqtl[,c('tf','OR','Pvalue')]
names(sqtl) <- c('tf','sQTL','s_p')
tf <- dplyr::left_join(aqtl,eqtl,by = 'tf')
tf <- dplyr::left_join(tf,sqtl,by = 'tf')
tf1 <- as.matrix(tf)
rownames(tf1) <- tf1[,1]
tf1 <- tf1[,-1]
tf11 <- apply(tf1[,1:6],2,as.numeric)
rownames(tf11) <- rownames(tf1)
tf11 <- tf11[!apply(tf11, 1, function(row) any(is.infinite(row))), ]
range(tf11[,c(1,3,5)])
range(tf11[,c(1)])
range(tf11[,c(3)])
range(tf11[,c(5)])
mycol1=colorRamp2(c(0, 1, 7),c( "#868686", "white", "#BC3C29"))
mycol2=colorRamp2(c(0, 1, 5),c( "#868686", "white", "#2D417F"))
mycol3=colorRamp2(c(0, 1, 5),c( "#868686", "white", "#CB812A"))

pdf(file = 'Figure 2C.pdf',height = 7.5,width = 7.5)
circos.par(gap.after=c(50))
circos.heatmap(as.matrix(tf11[,c(1)]),col=mycol1,dend.side= "inside",rownames.side= "outside",cell.border = T,bg.border="black", 
               rownames.col= "black",rownames.cex=1.5,rownames.font=1,track.height = 0.06,cluster=F)
circos.heatmap(tf11[,c(3)],col=mycol2,dend.side= "inside",cell.border = T,bg.border="black",
               rownames.side = NULL,track.height = 0.06,cluster=F)

circos.heatmap(tf11[,c(5)],col=mycol3,dend.side= "inside",cell.border = T,bg.border="black", 
               rownames.side = NULL,track.height = 0.06,cluster=F)
lg1=Legend(title="OR compared\nwith non-apaQTL",col_fun=mycol1,direction = c("horizontal"),)
lg2=Legend(title="OR compared\nwith non-eQTL",col_fun=mycol2,direction = c("horizontal"),)
lg3=Legend(title="OR compared\nwith non-sQTL",col_fun=mycol3,direction = c("horizontal"),)
lg_combined <- packLegend(lg1, lg2, lg3, direction = "vertical")
grid.draw(lg_combined)
circos.track(track.index=get.current.track.index(),panel.fun=function(x,y){
  cn=rev(colnames(tf11[,c(1,3,5)]))
  n=length(cn)
  circos.text(rep(-7.8,3)+convert_x(0.5,"mm"),
              c(1,2.3,3.8),
              cn,cex=1.5,adj=c(0,1),facing="inside")#}
},bg.border=NA)
circos.clear()
dev.off()

rm(list = ls())
library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)
library(ggrepel)  
dat1 <- read.csv('aqtl_RBP_fisher_res.csv')
dat1 <- subset(dat1,!type=='RBP_occupancy.bed')
dat1$type <- gsub('.bed','',dat1$type,fixed = T)
dat1 <- dat1[order(dat1$Pvalue),]

ggplot(dat1, aes(x = -log10(Pvalue), y = log2(OR))) +
  geom_point(aes(color = Pvalue < 0.05/200  & OR >1), size = 3.5) +  
  scale_color_manual(values = c("grey", "#BC3C29")) +   
  geom_vline(xintercept = -log10(0.05/200), linetype = "dashed", color = "black", size = 0.5) +  
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, color = "black", linetype = 2, linewidth = 0.5) +
  geom_text_repel(data = dat1[1:20,], aes(label = type), 
                  size = 5, box.padding = 0.3, max.overlaps = 20) +  
  labs(x = expression("-log"[10]*"("*italic("P")*")"), y = "log2(OR)\ncompared with non-apaQTL") +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(
    legend.position = "none",              
    axis.title = element_text(size = 18),   
    axis.text = element_text(size = 18)     
  )+
  ggtitle("Enrichment analysis of apaQTLs within\nbinding sites for RBP")

ggsave(file = 'Figure 2D.pdf',width = 7.2,height = 6.8)

cd /data1/qtl/code_for_submit/data/Fig2

R
library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)
library(tidyr)
rm(list = ls())

non_in_pas <- read.csv('non_aQTL_in_PAS_50bp.csv')
non_aqtl <- fread('non_aqtl.bed')
in_pas <- read.csv('aQTL_in_PAS_50bp.csv')
aqtl <- fread('aqtl.bed')
data <- matrix(c(length(unique(in_pas$V4)),  length(unique(non_in_pas$V4)), nrow(aqtl)-length(unique(in_pas$V4)), nrow(non_aqtl)-length(unique(non_in_pas$V4))), nrow = 2, byrow = TRUE)
colnames(data) <- c("QTL", "Non QTL")
rownames(data) <- c("IN", "Out")
result <- fisher.test(data, alternative = "two.sided")
fisher_res1 <- data.frame(Pvalue=result$p.value,OR=result$estimate,low_95_ci=result$conf.int[1],high_95_ci=result$conf.int[2])
fisher_res1$motif <- 'ALL'
polyA <- c('AAGAAA', 'AATAAA', 'AATACA', 'AATAGA', 'AATATA', 'AATGAA', 'ACTAAA', 'AGTAAA', 'ATTAAA', 'CATAAA', 'GATAAA', 'TATAAA', 'TTTAAA','AACAAA','AAAAAA')
aqtl_motif <- read.csv('aQTL_in_PAS_50bp.csv')
non_aqtl_motif <- read.csv('non_aQTL_in_PAS_50bp.csv')
aqtl_motif_res <- data.frame()
for (i in 1:length(polyA)) {
  dat1 <- subset(aqtl_motif,PAS_singal==polyA[i])
  res1 <- data.frame(motif = polyA[i],count_aqtl = nrow(dat1))
  aqtl_motif_res <- rbind(aqtl_motif_res,res1)
}
non_aqtl_motif_res <- data.frame()
for (i in 1:length(polyA)) {
  dat1 <- subset(non_aqtl_motif,PAS_singal==polyA[i])
  res1 <- data.frame(motif = polyA[i],count_non_aqtl = nrow(dat1))
  non_aqtl_motif_res <- rbind(non_aqtl_motif_res,res1)
}
res <- dplyr::left_join(aqtl_motif_res,non_aqtl_motif_res,by = 'motif')
for (i in 1:nrow(res)) {
  data <- matrix(c(res$count_aqtl[i], res$count_non_aqtl[i], nrow(aqtl)-res$count_aqtl[i], nrow(non_aqtl)-res$count_non_aqtl[i]), nrow = 2, byrow = TRUE)
  colnames(data) <- c("QTL", "Non QTL")
  rownames(data) <- c("IN", "Out")
  result <- fisher.test(data, alternative = "two.sided")
  fisher_res2 <- data.frame(Pvalue=result$p.value,OR=result$estimate,low_95_ci=result$conf.int[1],high_95_ci=result$conf.int[2])
  fisher_res2$motif <- res$motif[i]
  fisher_res1 <- rbind(fisher_res1,fisher_res2)
}
fisher_res1$neg_log10_p <- -log10(fisher_res1$Pvalue)
fisher_res1 <- dplyr::left_join(fisher_res1,res,by = 'motif')
fisher_res1$or_ci <- paste0(round(fisher_res1$OR,2),' (',round(fisher_res1$low_95_ci,2),'-',round(fisher_res1$high_95_ci,2),')')
fisher_res1$P <- round(fisher_res1$Pvalue,3)
write.csv(fisher_res1,file = 'fisher_res.csv',row.names = F)
fisher_res1 <- fisher_res1[-1,]
fisher_res1$count_aqtl <- fisher_res1$count_aqtl/10
fisher_res1 <- fisher_res1[order(fisher_res1$count_aqtl,decreasing = T),]
df_long <- fisher_res1 %>%
  pivot_longer(cols = c(count_aqtl,neg_log10_p), 
               names_to = "type", values_to = "value") %>%
  mutate(value = ifelse(type == "neg_log10_p", -value, value))
df_long$motif <- factor(df_long$motif,levels = fisher_res1$motif)

colors <- c(
  "AATAAA" = "#B8436D", 
  "AAAAAA" = "#7E3F8F",  
  "TTTAAA" = "#E26D5C", 
  "CATAAA" = "#F1993A", 
  "AATGAA" = "#D9C13E",  
  "AATATA" = "#B3C161",  
  "AATAGA" = "#6FAF74",  
  "GATAAA" = "#4A937D",  
  "ACTAAA" = "#358A9E",  
  "AGTAAA" = "#2D6FA3", 
  "ATTAAA" = "#3B4F9A",  
  "TATAAA" = "#504D84",  
  "AAGAAA" = "#705A8C", 
  "AACAAA" = "#926C90",  
  "AATACA" = "#AF7AA1" )

ggplot(df_long, aes(x = motif, y = value, fill = motif)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = position_dodge(width = 0.6), width = 0.75) + 
  scale_fill_manual(values = colors) + 
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, color = "black") +  
  geom_hline(yintercept = log10(0.05/15), linetype = "dashed", color = "red") + 
  labs(x = NULL, 
       y = expression("Log"[10]*"(P) / Motif Count")) +  
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    panel.grid = element_blank(), 
    axis.text.x = element_blank(), 
    axis.ticks.x = element_blank(), 
    axis.text.y = element_text(size = 18), 
    axis.ticks.y = element_line(color = "black"), 
    axis.line.y.left = element_line(color = "black"),  
    legend.text = element_text(size = 15),  
    axis.title.y = element_text(size = 18, margin = margin(r = 10))  
  )+
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(-6, max(df_long$value), by = 1))
